{"tid":1559430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全新兵種: 雜務兵","createTime":"2019-09-10T21:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:51:55.000Z","uid":246340,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32c45658f3d638acc500515e7952fa8619db3dd9","tid":1559430,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:18:52.000Z","msg":"Well 雖然個名冇咁型<br />\n但我覺得好有用<br />\n雖然小妹我唔係最勇武嗰種<br />\n但我都發夢喺前線岀現過<br />\n<br />\n由於冇大台<br />\n示威者嘅行動難免會比較混亂、低效率。<br />\n<br />\n以消息嘅傳遞為例<br />\n示威者較為依賴特定兵種:哨兵<br />\n但當有突發情況岀現時，沒有哨兵就令現場資訊十分混亂。<br />\n<br />\n908一役，在場遊行人士並沒有意識去留意附近情況。大多著眼於如何處理党鐵站岀口、如何獲得更多投擲物及障礙物。<br />\n<br />\n不久，有其他街口嘅遊行人士跑過嚟: <br />\n有狗清場吖！快啲走吖！<br />\n<br />\n呢個行為有幾點唔好:<br />\n1.資訊不足<br />\n冇確切狗隻數量、種類;狗隻嘅去向、行踪等。<br />\n<br />\n2.引起恐慌<br />\n慌張嘅情緒係會傳染，人嘅自然反應係走。<br />\n例子參考各狗隻清場片段。<br />\n<br />\n處理呢種情況要先安撫該名手足，<br />\n然後詳細詢問狗隻數量及去向:<br />\n軍裝定防暴？<br />\n有幾多個/車(EU定狗籠)？<br />\n由咩方向去咩方向？<br />\n<br />\n於現場以上問題基本夠用，少嘅唔洗驚，多嘅驚嚟冇用。<br />\n<br />\n我會先問清楚，然後自己去做哨兵，跑去附近街口問下其他手足咩環境。以獲得一手資訊去同其他手足講。<br />\n<br />\nsor for1999<br />\n我想表達嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好限死自己咩兵種</span><br />\n我地係超級唔夠人用<br />\n喺呢啲情況下 <br />\n必須咩都識啲<br />\n唔求精通，但要識要知<br />\n<br />\n冇哨兵/冇tg gp報料<br />\n就要有人去做哨兵<br />\n<br />\n唔夠人去set RB<br />\n就要有人頂上<br />\n<br />\n唔夠物資<br />\n就要有人負責搵物資返嚟<br />\n<br />\n我地冇大台<br />\n呢啲嘢一定要自發做<br />\n積少成多 聚沙成塔<br />\n每人做多少少 個效果就多好多<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n我地要煲底除罩相見架<br />\n有錯輕力啲屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a429c3e87afd8a5f27f3337996daac18de76aa4f","tid":1559430,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02325c25b49b89b57e7ceb2f48c5a7427dd9c87","tid":1559430,"uid":300977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:20:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a88511e9669ce537d54fbcd1bc7c3d4c3511afdb","tid":1559430,"uid":227174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc23a7a846a2a909bf8ab9dfeac32bf6c0b3c18","tid":1559430,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a88511e9669ce537d54fbcd1bc7c3d4c3511afdb","tid":1559430,"uid":227174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfa4ba9a563570b1d4a2e8954c511aabeaf91bb","tid":1559430,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aa532f2ffe1650c274574852efb7259fe597319","tid":1559430,"uid":289041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:27:18.000Z","msg":"p牌無得推。但你講得好岩"},{"pid":"f0f7e8286e195a2b3d3575234fa726029682c1f6","tid":1559430,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:28:17.000Z","msg":"幫手拎走啲物資<br />\n唔好俾狗充公"},{"pid":"e36ee3f2155643280837db0b5fcf367ee93e5381","tid":1559430,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:39:30.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5d78ef973bbb67fde54aa4b37a73379c778074b4","tid":1559430,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T21:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab2066b556aec2b27800e0b92d7ec54ccb19b34","tid":1559430,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:47:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f531608124f8d5c1f64a1d7393fc7fa4695721d7","tid":1559430,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"一上到最前線見到狗有人大叫「走呀，快啲走呀」<br />\n真係好影響士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同好驚<br />\n如果叫有狗嚟，大叫大家小心啲，各就各位，個反應會好唔同"},{"pid":"6d3e87fe36e2a42e3c3555e673f72db47f6f3162","tid":1559430,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6b7a71d958bc5868e8a3c8d7488adb976dbc1ae","tid":1559430,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"樓主正確<br />\n其實係要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0bab6baa96489b31fd688674798f71e55d597a","tid":1559430,"uid":287758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fK7PUjU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfK7PUjU.png&h=95c1ef6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">萬能俠</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[727] 游山玩水Online 佈陣 組織 戰術<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365941</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}